<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771105>
    dc:description "FIGURE 60. Male T7 of A) Anthophora curta (BBSL502199), B) A. erythrothorax (UCRCENT335472), C) A. escalante (BBSL1026857), D) A. estebana (BBSL273457), E) A. exigua (82025), F) A. flavocincta (BBSL504073). Scale=0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771115>
    dc:description "FIGURE 65. Male S7 of A) Anthophora curta (BBSL502426), B) A. erythrothorax (UCRCENT407167), C) A. escalante (BBSL585670), D) A. estebana (BBSL502606), E) A. exigua (BBSL502726), F) A. flavocincta (BBSL504089). Scale=0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771115/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771125>
    dc:description "FIGURE 70. Male S8 of A) Anthophora curta (BBSL502426), B) A. erythrothorax (UCRCENT335472), C) A. escalante (BBSL585670), D) A. estebana (BBSL502606), E) A. exigua (BBSL502726), F) A. flavocincta (BBSL504079). Scale=0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771135>
    dc:description "FIGURE 75. Male genital capsule of A) Anthophora curta (BBSL502426), B) A. erythrothorax (UCRCENT335472), C) A. escalante (BBSL585670), D) A. estebana (BBSL502607), E) A. exigua (82027), F) A. flavocincta (BBSL504079). Scale=0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771135/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771059>
    dc:description "FIGURE 38. Male sterna, S5 setae density and S6 rim form. Scale=0.5 mm. A) S5 with sparse setae; S6 medially emarginate, at least vaguely triangularly, evenly so (A. estebana, 72476). B) S5 setae density high, appearing tufted; S6 medially emarginate, at least vaguely triangularly, but at least slightly filled medially, sometimes tufted (A. maculifrons, 82068). C) S5 with sparse setae; S6 entire or nearly so, with transparent square of integument (A. petrophila, BBSL655748). D) S5 setae density high; S6 entire, medially knobbed (A. flavocincta, BBSL504065)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771059/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3771005>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Distribution of Anthophora curta. Generated with 2498 specimen records from 932 locations." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3771005/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

